These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite
2 different pets are kept: ferret, hamster
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, indian
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, sports
2 different games are played: poker, scrabble
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, volleyball
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, azalea
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the chinese##1
4. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | sprite     | hot-chocolate |
| Pet         | hamster  | ferret       |
| Nationality           | indian   | chinese    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports     | documentary   |
| Game   | scrabble      | poker     |
| Sport         | volleyball | swimming      |
| Flower     | azalea       | poppy           |

