.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, country
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, dahlia
The people have 2 different hobbies: cooking, camping
There are 2 different favourite colors: brown, coral
2 different pets are kept: cat, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, van
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the fan of country##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
5. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
| Beverage      | sprite         | cola       |
| Music-Genre          | trance        | country |
| Flower           | dahlia | sunflower    |
| Hobby   | camping        | cooking  |
| Color   | coral        | brown       |
| Pet           | rat            | cat        |
| Transport     | van            | ship       |

