3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating lemon is the person watching action movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
